    "SpeakerId": "Buck",
    "Text": "Ah, the Maze Race! Now there’s a story for the ages. Folks from all over bring their best wheels, hopin’ for a shot at glory. The Maze ain’t just a pile of dirt and turns—it’s a wild old place with more twists than a rattlesnake.[br]If you got the grit, you could win big. But first, you gotta pick yourself a ride. I got a few out back, and a test area where you can get the feel for ‘em.[br]Ready to see what you’re made of?",
